_sText:
This is my second map, plz don't use it to make your own.

The map can support 64 players but i recommend only 32 players cause it's not really big enough for 64.

I made the front yard a bit empty so the T's would've to play tactical to go into the house using smokes and flashbangs. Theres 2 tunnels, 1 goes to the side of the house and from there u can take a ladder onto the roof. The second tunnel goes to the middle of the front yard behind a few boxes, to the garage door (which is open) and to the basement (bombsite B).

Thank you Chizbone for fixing my .nav file.
